'''Netu Yukam''', according to [[Ayyavazhi mythology]], was a time when another fragment of [[Kroni]] was created into two wicked persons called [[Thillaimallalan]] and [[Mallosivahanan]]. They ruled over the people most wickedly by extracting [[Uliyam]] and [[Iraikal]] ([[taxes]]) from them. When it became unbearable, the [[Thevarkal]] (celestial beings) complained to [[Shiva|Isvaran]], who in turn commissioned [[Thirumal|Mayon]] to carry out the destruction of the wicked rulers, which he later did.

