'''''Zman Tel Aviv''''' ({{lang-he|זמן תל אביב}}, ''Tel Aviv Time'') is a weekly [[newspaper]] published in [[Tel Aviv]], [[Israel]].  The paper features content specific for the Tel Aviv area.

''Zman Tel Aviv'' is a [[Hebrew language]] paper featuring local culture articles.

